  <brief_title>Exercise-based Cardiac Rehabilitation After Thoracoscopic Ablation in Patients With Persisent Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Exercise-based Cardiac Rehabilitation Increase Physical Activity in Patients Who Undergoing Totally Thoracoscopic Ablation?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
